                        Caltrans Live Traffic Cameras

   [tv_top.jpg] [tv_left.jpg] [EMBED]
   [tv_right.jpg] [tv_bottom.jpg]

   Caltrans has over four hundred cameras monitoring freeway sections
   across California. Select the section of California you are interested
   in, then view the live streaming videos of traffic available for that
   region. Our Frequently Asked Questions page may answer other questions
   that you have about the Caltrans Traffic View pages.



